reviewText: Features 29 Playmates as they appear in different fashions designed by Betsey Johnson. Shows backstage as they change clothes and features clips of the models from when they disrobed on video.  A lot is going on as sometimes there are two and three images at a time to look at, clothed and unclothed side-by-side. Entertaining, watchable.

Playboy Playmates On The Catwalk - I'm Too Sexy is forty-eight minutes long. The video features Betsey Johnson and her daughter Lulu Johnson with the focus on Betsey Johnson's clothing design. Some of her clothes are pretty lame and not that exciting at all. Betsey uses twenty-seven Playmates for her fashion show. Most of them you don't see until the fashion show are over and they take that final walk on the runway. Some of the Playmates and focused and you see the nudity and most of the nudity you do see is old archive footage. They Playmates that do get the bulk of the time slot are Victoria Silvstedt, Carrie Stevens, Karin Taylor, Brooke Berry, Angel Boris, Suzanne Stokes and The Dahm Triplets (Nicole, Erica, and Jaclyn). The nudity only takes up 15% of the video and the rest of the time is spent in the changing, Betsey commenting on her fashion line, the Playmates on the catwalk, and some one to one interviews. I just thought it was boring. Playboy Playmates On The Catwalk - I'm Too Sexy get a D as is dud.
